body_content: PL25008aTLd: IMO MSC 110 5 - Papers 5 15, 5 16, 5 17, 5 18, 5 21 - To Review Date: 28 May 2025 To : Panel Chair Cc : Panel Members Subject: PL25008aTLd: IMO MSC 110 5 - Papers 5 15, 5 16, 5 17, 5 18, 5 21 - To Review Dear Chair and Panel Members, 1. Reference is made to PL25008aILf:. 2. MSC 110-5-18 Supported (MSC 110-5-18 and MSC 110-5-17(OCM) can be considered together in the working group) MSC 110-5-21 Not supported, high level requirement provided in the current version of 5.7 is preferred. analysis_result.summary: TL provides comments on IMO MSC 110 papers 5-15 through 5-21, indicating support, partial support, or non-support for each document.
